{
  "video_id": "_L052IOoX0Y",
  "title": "Reuben Margolin: Sculpting waves in wood and time",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 7000.0,
      "text": "Translator: Timothy Covell Reviewer: Morton Bast"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15260.0,
      "end_time": 17884.0,
      "text": "Usually I like working in my shop,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17885.0,
      "end_time": 22218.0,
      "text": "but when it&#39;s raining and the driveway outside turns into a river,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 22218.0,
      "end_time": 24258.0,
      "text": "then I just love it."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24258.0,
      "end_time": 27589.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;ll cut some wood and drill some holes and watch the water,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 27589.0,
      "end_time": 30468.0,
      "text": "and maybe I&#39;ll have to walk around and look for washers."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 30468.0,
      "end_time": 33400.0,
      "text": "You have no idea how much time I spend."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 33400.0,
      "end_time": 35427.0,
      "text": "This is the \"Double Raindrop.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 35427.0,
      "end_time": 38552.0,
      "text": "Of all my sculptures, it&#39;s the most talkative."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 43690.0,
      "end_time": 46702.0,
      "text": "It adds together the interference pattern"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 46702.0,
      "end_time": 49980.0,
      "text": "from two raindrops that land near each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 49981.0,
      "end_time": 55128.0,
      "text": "Instead of expanding circles, they&#39;re expanding hexagons."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 60205.0,
      "end_time": 64489.0,
      "text": "All the sculptures move by mechanical means."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 70150.0,
      "end_time": 74385.0,
      "text": "Do you see how there&#39;s three peaks to the yellow sine wave?"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 74385.0,
      "end_time": 80485.0,
      "text": "Right here I&#39;m adding a sine wave with four peaks and turning it on."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 95904.0,
      "end_time": 99369.0,
      "text": "Eight hundred two-liter soda bottles --"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 99370.0,
      "end_time": 101114.0,
      "text": "oh yea."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 101114.0,
      "end_time": 103350.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 113519.0,
      "end_time": 117177.0,
      "text": "Four hundred aluminum cans."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 119777.0,
      "end_time": 122537.0,
      "text": "Tule is a reed that&#39;s native to California,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 122537.0,
      "end_time": 127803.0,
      "text": "and the best thing about working with it is that it smells just delicious."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 141950.0,
      "end_time": 144430.0,
      "text": "A single drop of rain"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 144430.0,
      "end_time": 146558.0,
      "text": "increasing amplitude."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 168143.0,
      "end_time": 173369.0,
      "text": "The spiral eddy that trails a paddle on a rafting trip."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 183523.0,
      "end_time": 186398.0,
      "text": "This adds together four different waves."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 186398.0,
      "end_time": 189319.0,
      "text": "And here I&#39;m going to pull out the double wavelengths"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 189319.0,
      "end_time": 192667.0,
      "text": "and increase the single."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 192667.0,
      "end_time": 195608.0,
      "text": "The mechanism that drives it has nine motors"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 195608.0,
      "end_time": 198130.0,
      "text": "and about 3,000 pulleys."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 207776.0,
      "end_time": 212433.0,
      "text": "Four hundred and forty-five strings in a three-dimensional weave."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 212433.0,
      "end_time": 215272.0,
      "text": "Transferred to a larger scale --"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 215272.0,
      "end_time": 218350.0,
      "text": "actually a lot larger, with a lot of help --"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 218350.0,
      "end_time": 222117.0,
      "text": "14,064 bicycle reflectors --"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 222117.0,
      "end_time": 225866.0,
      "text": "a 20-day install."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 244943.0,
      "end_time": 246635.0,
      "text": "\"Connected\" is a collaboration"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 246635.0,
      "end_time": 250439.0,
      "text": "with choreographer Gideon Obarzanek."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 250439.0,
      "end_time": 253780.0,
      "text": "Strings attached to dancers."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 253780.0,
      "end_time": 256202.0,
      "text": "This is very early rehearsal footage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 256202.0,
      "end_time": 258564.0,
      "text": "but the finished work&#39;s on tour"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 258564.00000000003,
      "end_time": 262937.0,
      "text": "and is actually coming through L.A. in a couple weeks."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 267399.0,
      "end_time": 272431.0,
      "text": "A pair of helices and 40 wooden slats."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 293310.0,
      "end_time": 296260.0,
      "text": "Take your finger and draw this line."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 296260.0,
      "end_time": 300260.0,
      "text": "Summer, fall, winter, spring,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 300260.0,
      "end_time": 306497.0,
      "text": "noon, dusk, dark, dawn."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 306497.0,
      "end_time": 309760.0,
      "text": "Have you ever seen those stratus clouds"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 309760.0,
      "end_time": 312433.0,
      "text": "that go in parallel stripes across the sky?"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 312433.0,
      "end_time": 315280.0,
      "text": "Did you know that&#39;s a continuous sheet of cloud"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 315280.0,
      "end_time": 318625.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s dipping in and out of the condensation layer?"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 318625.0,
      "end_time": 321458.0,
      "text": "What if every seemingly isolated object"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 321458.0,
      "end_time": 325302.0,
      "text": "was actually just where the continuous wave of that object"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 325302.0,
      "end_time": 328783.0,
      "text": "poked through into our world?"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 328783.0,
      "end_time": 333160.0,
      "text": "The Earth is neither flat nor round."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 333160.0,
      "end_time": 337583.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s wavy."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 337583.0,
      "end_time": 343810.0,
      "text": "It sounds good, but I&#39;ll bet you know in your gut that it&#39;s not the whole truth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 343810.0,
      "end_time": 344639.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;ll tell you why."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 344639.0,
      "end_time": 346635.0,
      "text": "I have a two-year-old daughter who&#39;s the best thing ever."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 346635.0,
      "end_time": 348718.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;m just going to come out and say it:"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 348718.0,
      "end_time": 352253.0,
      "text": "My daughter is not a wave."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 352253.0,
      "end_time": 356832.0,
      "text": "And you might say, \"Surely, Rueben, if you took even just the slightest step back,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 356833.0,
      "end_time": 359593.0,
      "text": "the cycles of hunger and eating,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 359593.0,
      "end_time": 362433.0,
      "text": "waking and sleeping, laughing and crying"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 362433.0,
      "end_time": 365440.0,
      "text": "would emerge as pattern.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 365440.0,
      "end_time": 367671.0,
      "text": "But I would say, \"If I did that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 367671.0,
      "end_time": 371159.0,
      "text": "too much would be lost.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 371160.0,
      "end_time": 375889.0,
      "text": "This tension between the need to look deeper"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 375889.0,
      "end_time": 378843.0,
      "text": "and the beauty and immediacy of the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 378843.0,
      "end_time": 382545.0,
      "text": "where if you even try to look deeper you&#39;ve already missed what you&#39;re looking for,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 382545.0,
      "end_time": 385616.0,
      "text": "this tension is what makes the sculptures move."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 385616.0,
      "end_time": 388127.0,
      "text": "And for me, the path between these two extremes"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 388127.0,
      "end_time": 390862.0,
      "text": "takes the shape of a wave."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 390862.0,
      "end_time": 393929.0,
      "text": "Let me show you one more."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 435360.0,
      "end_time": 438789.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much. Thanks."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 438789.0,
      "end_time": 440969.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 440970.0,
      "end_time": 442202.0,
      "text": "Thanks."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 442202.0,
      "end_time": 446666.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 446666.0,
      "end_time": 448439.0,
      "text": "June Cohen: Looking at each of your sculptures,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 448439.0,
      "end_time": 450867.0,
      "text": "they evoke so many different images."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 450867.0,
      "end_time": 453402.0,
      "text": "Some of them are like the wind and some are like waves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 453402.0,
      "end_time": 456287.0,
      "text": "and sometimes they look alive and sometimes they seem like math."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 456287.0,
      "end_time": 458791.0,
      "text": "Is there an actual inspiration behind each one?"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 458791.0,
      "end_time": 462347.0,
      "text": "Are you thinking of something physical or somthing tangible as you design it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 462347.0,
      "end_time": 465486.0,
      "text": "RM: Well some of them definitely have a direct observation --"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 465487.0,
      "end_time": 468302.0,
      "text": "like literally two raindrops falling,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 468302.0,
      "end_time": 471177.0,
      "text": "and just watching that pattern is so stunning."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 471177.0,
      "end_time": 476866.0,
      "text": "And then just trying to figure out how to make that using stuff."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 476881.0,
      "end_time": 479409.0,
      "text": "I like working with my hands."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 479425.0,
      "end_time": 481635.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s nothing better than cutting a piece of wood"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 481635.0,
      "end_time": 483385.0,
      "text": "and trying to make it move."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 483385.0,
      "end_time": 485135.0,
      "text": "JC: And does it ever change?"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 485135.0,
      "end_time": 486260.0,
      "text": "Do you think you&#39;re designing one thing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 486260.0,
      "end_time": 488100.0,
      "text": "and then when it&#39;s produced it looks like something else?"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 488100.0,
      "end_time": 491468.0,
      "text": "RM: The \"Double Raindrop\" I worked on for nine months,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 491468.0,
      "end_time": 493794.0,
      "text": "and when I finally turned it on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 493825.0,
      "end_time": 497467.0,
      "text": "I actually hated it."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 497468.0,
      "end_time": 501593.0,
      "text": "The very moment I turned it on, I hated it."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 501593.0,
      "end_time": 504941.0,
      "text": "It was like a really deep-down gut reaction, and I wanted to throw it out."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 504941.0,
      "end_time": 507850.0,
      "text": "And I happened to have a friend who was over,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 507850.0,
      "end_time": 509970.0,
      "text": "and he said, \"Why don&#39;t you just wait.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 509970.0,
      "end_time": 513466.0,
      "text": "And I waited, and the next day I liked it a bit better,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 513466.0,
      "end_time": 516427.0,
      "text": "the next day I liked it a bit better, and now I really love it."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 516427.0,
      "end_time": 521930.0,
      "text": "And so I guess, one, the gut reactions a little bit wrong sometimes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 521919.99999999994,
      "end_time": 523634.99999999994,
      "text": "and two, it does not look like as expected."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 523635.0,
      "end_time": 526520.0,
      "text": "JC: The relationship evolves over time."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 526520.0,
      "end_time": 526927.0,
      "text": "Well thank you so much. That was a gorgeous treat for us."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 526927.0,
      "end_time": 529814.0,
      "text": "RM: Thanks. (JC: Thank you, Reuben.)"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 529814.0,
      "end_time": 532177.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}